			<description><![CDATA[<p class="evidence_indonesian">Saya Rina Ocvita ingin bercerita tentang kehidupan pribadi saya, di mulai dari sebuah keluarga yang sangat bahagia. Ayah saya bernama Ridwan Ibbas Kepala Laboratorium Perikanan Lampulo. Ibu saya bernama Nurllaila dan saya memiliki 2 orang adik yang bernama Muammal Mirza dan Agam Fauzan. Pada tanggal 26 Desember 2004 Gempa dan tsunami telah menghancurkan dan meluluhlantakkan semua fasilitas, sarana dan prasarana yang ada serta ratus ribu ummat manusia meninggal dunia akibat ditimpa musibah berupa gempa bumi dan gelombang tsunami yang maha dahsyat yang Allah berikan sebagai peringatan bagi hambanya.

Pada pagi Minggu tanggal 26 Desember 2004 kami sekeluarga berkumpul di rumah, pada pukul 08.00 wib saat gempa terjadi yang sungguh sangat kuat. Kami sekeluarga merasa takut dan keluar dari rumah duduk di halaman depan, tak lama kemudian kami melihat ada orang berlarian sambil berteriak air laut naik - air laut naik….begitu terus yang kami dengar. Bapak saya berkata ayo kita lari naik mobil, kami semua pun masuk kedalam mobil dan pergi dari rumah, di dalam perjalanan saya melihat banyak orang orang berlarian dan tiba-tiba bapak membelokkan mobil ke jalan buntu. Bapak berkata turun-turun cepat dari mobil karena air lautnya sudah meluap dari sungai, saya bersama adik dan ibu terjebak di dalam bobil tidak bisa keluar. Namun akhirnya dengan pertolongan Allah kami dapat juga keluar dari mobil dan berlarian keluar. Saat itu saya melihat adik saya Agam Fauzan di gendong oleh Bapak dan mereka naik ke atas pagar. Saya panggil Bapak, Bapak, Bapak, tapi beliau tidak memberikan jawaban apapun kemudian saya terus berlari bersama ibu dan adik saya Muammal Mirza dan kamipun naik ke rumah Pak Muhammad. Tidak lama kemudian kami menyaksikan bapak dan adik kami yang kecil Agam Fauzan di gulung ombak gelombang tsunami, kami ingin menolong tapi tidak bisa karna arusnya terlalu deras. Kami juga dibawa arus karena rumahnya hampir tenggelam, sehingga kami terdampar di atas atap rumah. Tiba-tiba datang Bapak Khalik, beliau mengajak kami naik ke atas kapal yang tersangkut di rumah Ibu Abes, dari atas kapal saya melihat kedahsyatan gelombang tsunami meluluh lantakkan semua sraana dan prasarana yang ada baik rumah dan bangunan-bangunan lainnya. Kami semua yang berada di atas bot hanya bisa berdoa dan memohon ampun kepada Allah SWT semoga ini semua bukanlah akhir dari dunia ini.

Pada pukul 03.00 wib airpun mulai suurut sedikit demi sedikit. Semua orang yang berada di atas kapal merasakkan kelaparan dan kehausan tiba-tiba datang Bang Dani memberikan kami semua buah kelapa yang entah dari mana dia dapatkan. Pada pukul 04.00 wib kami semua pun turun dari boat menuju ke kota, sesampai di RS Kesdam kami di tolong oleh keluarga Bang Zulfikar dan kamipun dibawa ke Indrapuri. Disanalah kami mengungsi sementara, sedangkan rumah harta benda dan orang tua kami tercinta serta adik kami tersayang telah dipanggil oleh Allah SWT. Semoga bapak dan adik kami Agam Fauzan mendapat tempat yang layak disisi Allah SWT, diterima amal ibadahnya dan di ampuni segala dosanya. Amin ya Rabbal Alamin.
.</p>
			<p class="evidence_english">My name is Rina Ocvita, I want to tell you about my personal life, start of a very happy family. My father named Ridwan Ibbas, Chief Fisheries Laboratory of Lampulo. My mother named Nurllaila and I had 2 brothers named Muammal Fauzan Mirza and Agam. On December 26, 2004 earthquake and tsunami had destroyed and devastated all of the amenities, facilities and infrastructure as well as hundreds of thousands of human beings died from a giant earthquake and tsunami, that Allah almighty gave it to us as a warning to his servant.

On Sunday morning December 26, 2004 our family gathered at home, at 08.00 pm when the earthquake occurred is indeed very strong. Our whole family felt scared and out of the house sitting in the front yard. Not long after, we saw people running while screaming &quot;sea water rising - rising sea water ...&quot;, it was continues what we&apos;ve heard. My father said &quot;Let&apos;s running by the car&quot;, all of us into the car and went from our house. On the way, I saw a lot of peoples were running and suddenly my father turned the car into a dead end. My father said, &quot;Get out from the car quickly because the sea water has overflowed from the river&quot;, along with my mother and my brother we were trapped inside the car can not get out. But finally with the help of Allah we can also got out of the car and ran out. At that time I saw my father carrying my brother, Agam Fauzan, they climbed up to the top of the fence. I called him, &quot;Father...father...father...&quot;, but he did not give any answer then I kept running with my mother and my brother Muammal Mirza and we were also climbed up to the house of Mr Muhammad. 
Not long after this,  we watched our father and younger brother Agam Fauzan were rolled by tsunami waves, we wanted to help but could not because the water current was too swift. We were also carried by currents because the house was almost drowned, so we were stranded on the roof of the house. Suddenly came Mr. Khalik, he took us up to the top of the stuck ship at the house of Mrs. Abes, from the ship I saw an awesomeness tsunami,  devastated all the amenities, facilities and infrastructure both houses and other buildings. All of us were  above the bot can only pray and ask forgiveness to Allah SWT, I hope this all was not the end of the world.

At 03.00 pm the water had started to recede little by little. All the people who were on board feel the hunger and thirst, suddenly came Bang Dani gave all of us the coconuts that we did not know came from where. At 04.00 pm we all came down from the boat to the city, when we reached the Kesdam hospital, we followed Bang Zulfikar who brought us to his family in Indrapuri. Therein we evacuate temporarily, while the house property and our beloved parents and dear brother have been called by Allah. Hopefully our father and younger brother Agam  Fauzan got a decent place beside Allah SWT, accepted his good deeds and forgive all his sins. Amin Ya Rabbal Alamin.</p>]]></description>
